title: TLS 1.3 Handshake

participant Client as C
participant Server as S

note over C: Generate ephemeral key pair
C->>S: ClientHello (versions, key_share, ciphers)
note over S: Select cipher suite, generate keys
S-->>C: ServerHello (version, key_share)
S-->>C: EncryptedExtensions
S-->>C: Certificate
S-->>C: CertificateVerify (signature)
S-->>C: Finished (HMAC)
note over C: Verify cert chain + signature
C->>S: Finished (HMAC)
note over C, S: Derive application traffic keys
C->>S: Application Data (encrypted)
S-->>C: Application Data (encrypted)
